{"tid":2500036,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[鬥地主] 新界東北貨櫃屋戶主遭收地　居民稱已逆權侵佔　地政指不符安置資格","createTime":"2021-04-22T10:28:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T13:04:10.000Z","uid":173921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c8aeeeb7dc5428728036e9643a353c5e03dc14bc","tid":2500036,"uid":173921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T10:28:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSc2ZZ4KwmNXdgfN9hAzvKeseLqDbKJXhvC5QEriwSknf?filename=YpivQD7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYpivQD7.png&h=e246dfaf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新界東北發展計劃展開收地，居住在粉嶺塘坑村貨櫃屋的梁志倫向《立場新聞》表示，擁有地段業權的父親尚未與地政談妥特惠津貼及安置問題，惟昨早(21)突有政府人員帶同約30名工人來收地。他指，父親自 80 年代已在該處設辦公室工作，自己一家四口，包括僅七個月大的兒子亦居住在此處，批評「政府夾硬嚟&hellip;好明顯係強拆」。地政總署今日(22日)回覆指，已通知有關土地佔用人，須於去年9月30日前停止佔用。署方昨天展開跨部門清理土地行動，並已把相關土地移交土木工程拓展署。<br />\n<br />\n報道連結：<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3ehsBgs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3ehsBgs&d=0rs6uxY5NhpkL%2Fcp6PdBrX9Z9R%2B5WvgLevJIGZbvuGo%3D&h=505f1eff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3ehsBgs</a>"},{"pid":"c635a08413f7bb10679c0593e88cb6cc8693b7b1","tid":2500036,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T11:04:13.000Z","msg":"Yeah"},{"pid":"021dad05edc39bf07c9b6b728f9f76f8988aceb9","tid":2500036,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T12:25:01.000Z","msg":"寮屋豬狗, 應該全部槍斃！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aca08085c6850759b9ec1acd451467315e45728d","tid":2500036,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T12:57:45.000Z","msg":"官地要連續用60年先可以侵佔？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm